COMPONENT NAME: LKM HBase to Hive HBASE-SERDE COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.1.3.0.1 and above DESCRIPTION: This LKM provides read access to a HBase table from the Hive. This is achieved by defining a temporary load table definition on Hive which represents all relevant columns of the HBase source table.
Please see BigDataConnector Documentation for more details.
SNP_TRT : HiveBaseLKM #SNP_LINETRT : Drop Temporary Indexes on Stage
SNP_TRT : HiveBaseLKM #SNP_LINETRT : Create Temporary Indexes on Stage
